reviews.review:
Hello!

I would like to express my sincere gratitude for the development of the Rematch game. The project turned out to be exciting and of high quality.

 Let me suggest an idea for improving the gaming experience: introducing a replay (review) function for past matches. This feature will allow players to:

analyze tactics and strategies;

identify mistakes and improve their skills;

share interesting moments with friends;

relive memorable game episodes.

I am confident that this feature will increase user engagement and make the gameplay even more interesting. Thank you for considering this proposal!
